SIMPLE: assured
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Assured
<hw>As*sured"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Made sure; safe;
insured; certain; indubitable; not doubting; bold to excess.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Assured</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Assured
<hw>As*sured"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One whose life or property is
insured.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Assuredly</ent>⟦br⟧
